val jdks = List("OracleJDK8", "GraalEE", "GraalCE", "AdoptOpenJDK8Hotspot", "AdoptOpenJDKOpenJ9", "OpenJDK11Hotspot", "OpenJDK11Graal", "GraalEEC2")

val size = "1k"

val csvFile = "/Users/cguntur/projects/jvms-compare/benchmark-results/*/01*.csv"
val benchmarkData = spark.read.option("header", "true").csv(csvFile)
var df = benchmarkData.toDF("Benchmark", "Mode", "Threads", "Samples", "Score", "Error", "Units")
df = df.withColumn("JDK", when($"Mode".isNull, "").otherwise(jdks(0)))
df = df.withColumn("Benchmark", substring($"Benchmark", 23, 200))
var dataFrame = df.withColumn("Size", when($"Mode".isNull, "").otherwise("1 Thousand"))

for (i <- 2 to 8) {
    val csvFile = "/Users/cguntur/projects/jvms-compare/benchmark-results/*/0" + i + "*.csv"
    val benchmarkData = spark.read.option("header", "true").csv(csvFile)
    var df = benchmarkData.toDF("Benchmark", "Mode", "Threads", "Samples", "Score", "Error", "Units")
    df = df.withColumn("JDK", when($"Mode".isNull, "").otherwise(jdks(i - 1)))
    df = df.withColumn("Benchmark", substring($"Benchmark", 23, 200))
    df = df.withColumn("Size", when($"Mode".isNull, "").otherwise("1 Thousand"))
    dataFrame = dataFrame.union(df)
}

dataFrame.registerTempTable("benchmarks")
